{"about_the_game":"<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213700/extras/gif_banner__4_.gif?t=1701265706\" /><br><br><strong>Spirit of the North</strong> is a single-player 3rd-person adventure game inspired by the breathtaking and mysterious landscapes of Iceland. The story takes root from various pieces of<i> Nordic </i>folklore. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213700/extras/gif_banner__1_.gif?t=1701265706\" /><br><br>Play as an ordinary red fox whose story becomes entwined with the guardian of the Northern Lights, a magical spirit fox. As you journey over the mountains and under red-stained skies, you\u2019ll discover more about your companion and land left in ruin.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213700/extras/gif_banner__3_.gif?t=1701265706\" /><br><br>Uniquely designed to purposefully have no dialog or narration. Players must breathe in their surroundings to solve various puzzles and speculate the meaning of a lost ancient civilization.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213700/extras/gif_banner__2_.gif?t=1701265706\" /><br><br><strong><i>'touching &amp; memorable' - GamingBolt</i></strong><br><strong><i>'[...] a journey well worth taking' - TechRaptor</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2>- Make your way across stunning landscapes, on an emotionally stirring journey.<br><br><br>- Solve environmental puzzles to change the world around you, using ancient powers bestowed upon you by the guardian of the Northern Lights.<br><br>- Follow the mysterious Spirit Fox across a land left in ruin as you discover more about a lost civilization.<br><br>- Moving orchestral soundtrack featuring 14 original compositions.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Infused with Light","path":"https